{"tid":2363280,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"鄧炳強：對中大生襲學校保安感心痛憤怒","createTime":"2021-01-12T05:47:02.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-12T06:09:00.000Z","uid":20933,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"58b2e6f7b3ec7be1df95c29648b3f085ed91d932","tid":2363280,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T05:47:02.000Z","msg":"政府在啟德社區會堂設立的新型冠狀病毒個案追蹤辦公室昨日（11日）開始運作，今早（12日）近11時半，警務處長鄧炳強到啟德社區會堂了解辦公室運作，逗留約35分鐘後離開。<br />\n<br />\n鄧炳強離開前向在場傳媒表示，今日來訪主要了解警方人員工作情況，以及對他們協助抗疫表達感激。他並主動提到昨日中文大學有學生被捕一事，稱對黑衣暴徒襲擊保安感憤怒，事件中拘捕一中大學生。鄧炳強稱自己作為中大校友對此事感心痛，稱師弟的行為有違「博文約禮」校訓，達不到人類基本良知要求，也令其他優秀中大學生及畢業生難受，呼籲其他中大校友譴責事件。"},{"pid":"654b40115aebcbb4835549871754097401b2930d","tid":2363280,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T05:54:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0743c3014a8a11d055ed4453ebd7058b5a107e71","tid":2363280,"uid":60545,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T06:00:01.000Z","msg":"黑警學人講良知<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d20d9facfd96b25b26ee14eaab3210cb3110310","tid":2363280,"uid":55493,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T06:01:09.000Z","msg":"屌 誠明呀仆街！"},{"pid":"17d6238a81231588445dbcc808f1c2879cc6c6c8","tid":2363280,"uid":159392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T06:02:18.000Z","msg":"乜撚嘢都要加把口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed4017bc12f35394306f01df0011ff692cdea217","tid":2363280,"uid":14422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T06:02:39.000Z","msg":"喺香港唔需要有所謂嘅良知<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"751827628556d25853dcf6f53b5e51ddbc58f7f8","tid":2363280,"uid":261873,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T06:05:47.000Z","msg":"帶兵攻打中大就好開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 